# ── Plugin binaries (whitelisted) ────────────────────────────────────────────
# The patterns above (*.exe, *.dll, [Bb]in/, [Pp]ublish/) would otherwise hide
# the self-contained .NET binaries we DO want to ship inside plugins/<name>/bin/.
# These three lines un-ignore everything under that subtree so the marketplace
# can serve compiled artifacts.
!plugins/**/bin/
!plugins/**/bin/**
!plugins/**/bin/**/*
